{
  "texts": [
    "We fine-tune a GPT-3.5 Turbo model for Response Analyzer.",
    "The therapist also labeled and analyzed the output of Guides and Validator.We will open source the prompts we constructed as well as the datasets constructed by the psychotherapists.",
    "We did not conduct microbenchmark tests on basic LLM tasks such as the Rephraser and ReflectiveSummarizer.",
    "The former task involves structural rather than semantic rephrasing, while the latter repeats and converts statements from the first person to the third person.",
    "CaiTI's QuestionerCaiTI's Questioner drives the conversations based on Epsilon-Greedy Q-learning and a GPT-based \"Rephraser\"."
  ]
}